 it has in this case four heads. So that one turns out to be easy and that's the first one that we're

00:04:26.960 --> 00:04:34.000
 going to do. But when I wrote this, I mean, I knew what I was doing. I knew what a tree was. I knew

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:38.240
 what a hash was. That's the easy part. The hard part's writing the code. Now taking the code from

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:43.760
 someone else, like if you're taking it from Python or C++ or Java, that's easy. Thank heaven. They

